    f&amp;#x27;(x) &amp;amp;= \frac {(2x \cos x - x^2 \sin x - \frac 1 x)(\sqrt x + 3) - (x^2 \cos x - \ln x)(\frac 1 {2\sqrt x})} {(\sqrt x + 3)^2}
    \end{aligned}
