    (\cosh x)&amp;#x27; &amp;amp;= \left(\frac {e^x + e^{-x}} 2\right)&amp;#x27; \\
    &amp;amp;= \frac {e^x - e^{-x}} 2 = \sinh x
    \end{aligned}
