    f&amp;#x27;_-(0) = \lim_{\Delta x \to 0^-} \frac {|\Delta x|^\delta\cos\frac 1 {\Delta x}} {\Delta x} = -\lim_{\Delta x \to 0^-} |\Delta x|^{\delta - 1}\cos \frac 1 {\Delta x} = 0
